text: European Super League may refer to: ==Sports== * Super League (legal name: Super League Europe Ltd.), the top division of the European rugby league system since 1995 * Proposals for a European Super League in association football, a proposed league involving Europe's leading association football teams ** European Super League Company, S.L, a planned association football European Super League founded in 2021 * Eastern European Super League, an international American football tournament involving the best clubs from Russia and Belarus ==Entertainment== * European Superleague, an association football sports management video game
title: European Super League
